DbpL33fyMju5deb5LyeVg">Văn Ích thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-t%C3%ACnh-bi%E1%BB%83u/poem-AGKUOTf4MNBoRtTrY2zw2A">Trần tình biểu - 陳情表</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/author-2WZpsdSFEWvTQerf8uTifQ">Lý Mật</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Danh-%C3%81n/T%E1%BB%B1-th%C3%A1n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-QJK74_J02inWJMEPxc2HOg">Tự thán kỳ 2 - 自歎其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Danh-%C3%81n/author-7tg_rhleFYVL5Ann2EB2iA">Trần Danh Án</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-T%E1%BA%AFc/V%C3%A3n-An-Nam-qu%E1%BB%91c-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-gDpkQmlqpegDx6Ni4LwR9w">Vãn An Nam quốc vương - 挽安南國王</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-T%E1%BA%AFc/author-SdALrlg8daTfB8oNiho-Nw">Lê Tắc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
